{"article_id":"zj0MZ0HxGvAzBxjW","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Why did President Trump fire FBI Director James Comey ?","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"The president and top administration officials have offered contradictory accounts in recent days :","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"The official White House statement on May 9 said","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"Trump \" acted","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"based on the clear recommendations \" of the attorney general and deputy attorney general .","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"But Trump , in an interview two days later , said","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"he was going to fire Comey","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"\" regardless of recommendation . \"","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"Trump said","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"the \" FBI has been in turmoil , \"","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"and a White House spokeswoman said","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"\" the rank and file of the FBI had lost confidence \" in Comey .","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"\" That is not accurate , \"","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"according to Acting FBI Director Andrew McCabe ,","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"who said","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"Comey \" enjoyed broad support within the FBI ,","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"and still does to this day . \"","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"Trump fired Comey on May 9 .","depth":4},{"id":18,"text":"The White House issued a statement","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"saying ,","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"\" President Trump acted","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"based on the clear recommendations of both Deputy Attorney General Rod Rosenstein and Attorney General Jeff Sessions . \"","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"Rosenstein wrote a two-and-a-half page memo with the subject line \" Restoring Public Confidence in the FBI \"","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"that stated the reasons","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"why Comey should be removed .","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"The memo cited Comey ' s \" handling of the conclusion of the investigation of Secretary [ Hillary ] Clinton ' s emails. \"","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"Rosenstein criticized Comey","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"for holding a press conference on July 5 , 2016 ,","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"to publicly announce his recommendation","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"not to charge Clinton ,","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"and for announcing on Oct. 28 , 2016 ,","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"that the FBI had reopened its investigation of Clinton .","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"Comey ' s firing came","depth":4},{"id":33,"text":"less than two months after the director confirmed at a congressional hearing on March 20","depth":6},{"id":34,"text":"that the bureau is investigating","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"\" whether there was any coordination between the [ Trump ] campaign and Russia ' s efforts \"","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"to influence the 2016 presidential election .","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"In January , the Office of the Director of National Intelligence released a declassified intelligence report","depth":6},{"id":38,"text":"that found","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"\" Russian President Vladimir Putin ordered an influence campaign in 2016","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"aimed at the US presidential election \"","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"with the goal","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"of hurting Clinton","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"and helping to elect Trump .","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"Democrats have criticized the timing of Comey ' s firing ,","depth":5},{"id":45,"text":"because of the ongoing investigation .","depth":5},{"id":46,"text":"But Trump administration officials said","depth":5},{"id":47,"text":"the decision had nothing to do with Russia .","depth":5},{"id":48,"text":"On the night of Comey ' s firing , CNN ' s Anderson Cooper asked White House Counselor Kellyanne Conway ,","depth":6},{"id":49,"text":"\" Why fire James Comey now ? \"","depth":6},{"id":50,"text":"She cited Rosenstein ' s letter and his bipartisan credentials ,","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"noting","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"that he was overwhelmingly confirmed as deputy attorney general .","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"Conway , May 9 :","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"`` Well , I would point them to the three letters","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"that were received today , Anderson , the letter by President Donald Trump and letter by Attorney General Sessions and really the underlying report by Deputy Attorney General Rod Rosenstein ,","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"who the FBI director reports to ,","depth":13},{"id":57,"text":"the FBI director traditionally reports to the deputy attorney general .","depth":13},{"id":58,"text":"Rod Rosenstein was confirmed just 14 days ago by a vote of 94 to 6 by United States senators .","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"He ' s well-respected across both sides of the aisle .","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"He served as U.S. attorney in Maryland under President Obama .","depth":13},{"id":61,"text":"And he sent out a memo today to the attorney general","depth":14},{"id":62,"text":"and the re line , Anderson , says","depth":15},{"id":63,"text":"'restoring public confidence in the FBI . ' ``","depth":15},{"id":64,"text":"Conway said","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"Trump \" took the recommendation of his deputy attorney general ,","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"who oversees the FBI director . \"","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"Later in the interview , Cooper said","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"that \" a lot of people are ... saying","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"it destroys people ' s confidence in the FBI \" and its ability","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"to investigate","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"whether Trump aides colluded with Russia","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"to interfere in last year ' s election .","depth":12},{"id":73,"text":"Conway said","depth":5},{"id":74,"text":"the firing \" had zero to do \" with Russia","depth":6},{"id":75,"text":"and \" everything to do with ... Mr. Rosenstein . \"","depth":6},{"id":76,"text":"The next morning , on CNN ' s New Day , Conway repeated the claim :","depth":5},{"id":77,"text":"\" The president took the advice of the deputy attorney general","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"who oversees the director of the FBI ,","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"brought those concerns to the attorney general","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"who brought them to the president .","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"And they made a decision","depth":7},{"id":82,"text":"to remove him . \"","depth":7},{"id":83,"text":"On MSNBC ' s Morning Joe that same morning , White House deputy press secretary Sarah Huckabee Sanders echoed the official White House statement and Conway ' s remarks","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"when she was asked","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"why Comey was fired .","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"Sanders , May 10 :","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"`` I think","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"he ' s heard from the rank and file of the FBI , but particularly someone","depth":13},{"id":89,"text":"who had done a thorough review","depth":13},{"id":90,"text":"and someone","depth":13},{"id":91,"text":"who has the respect and reputation","depth":14},{"id":92,"text":"that the deputy attorney general has ,","depth":14},{"id":93,"text":"he took that seriously .","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"He took the recommendation seriously .","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"And he made a decision","depth":12},{"id":96,"text":"based on that . ''","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"Trump , however , told NBC ' s Lester Holt in a May 11 interview","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"that he did not base his decision on Rosenstein ' s recommendation .","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"Holt , May 11 :","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"`` Monday you met with the Deputy Attorney General Rod Rosenstein . ''","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"Trump :","depth":12},{"id":102,"text":"`` Right . ''","depth":12},{"id":103,"text":"Holt :","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"`` Did you ask for a recommendation ? ''","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"Trump :","depth":13},{"id":106,"text":"`` What I did is , I was going to fire Comey .","depth":14},{"id":107,"text":"My decision .","depth":14},{"id":108,"text":"It was not - ''","depth":12},{"id":109,"text":"Holt :","depth":13},{"id":110,"text":"`` You had made the decision","depth":14},{"id":111,"text":"before they came in the room . ''","depth":14},{"id":112,"text":"Trump :","depth":14},{"id":113,"text":"`` I was going to fire Comey .","depth":14},{"id":114,"text":"There ' s no good time","depth":17},{"id":115,"text":"to do it , by the way . ''","depth":17},{"id":116,"text":"Holt :","depth":17},{"id":117,"text":"`` Because in your letter you said ,","depth":18},{"id":118,"text":"' I accepted their recommendation . ' ''","depth":18},{"id":119,"text":"Trump :","depth":16},{"id":120,"text":"`` Well , they also - ''","depth":16},{"id":121,"text":"Holt :","depth":16},{"id":122,"text":"`` So , you had already made the decision . ''","depth":16},{"id":123,"text":"Trump :","depth":16},{"id":124,"text":"`` Oh , I was going to fire","depth":17},{"id":125,"text":"regardless of recommendation . ''","depth":17},{"id":126,"text":"The president told Holt ,","depth":10},{"id":127,"text":"\" The FBI has been in turmoil .","depth":11},{"id":128,"text":"You know that ,","depth":13},{"id":129,"text":"I know that .","depth":13},{"id":130,"text":"Everybody knows that .","depth":12},{"id":131,"text":"You take a look at the FBI a year ago ,","depth":10},{"id":132,"text":"it was in virtual turmoil , less than a year ago .","depth":11},{"id":133,"text":"It hasn ' t recovered from that . \"","depth":11},{"id":134,"text":"Trump and others in the administration have repeatedly made the claim","depth":9},{"id":135,"text":"that Comey had lost the confidence and respect of the FBI ' s rank and file .","depth":9},{"id":136,"text":"In addition to Trump saying","depth":10},{"id":137,"text":"the FBI has been in \" turmoil , \" Conway on CNN ' s New Day said","depth":10},{"id":138,"text":"that \" Jim Comey had lost the confidence of people at the FBI . \"","depth":9},{"id":139,"text":"At a May 10 press briefing , Sanders said","depth":11},{"id":140,"text":"the president , members of Congress and the Department of Justice had lost confidence in Comey .","depth":11},{"id":141,"text":"\" And most importantly , the rank and file of the FBI had lost confidence in their director , \"","depth":11},{"id":142,"text":"Sanders said .","depth":11},{"id":143,"text":"McCabe","depth":12},{"id":144,"text":"- a 21-year FBI official","depth":13},{"id":145,"text":"who assumed the position of acting FBI director","depth":14},{"id":146,"text":"when Comey was fired -","depth":14},{"id":147,"text":"was asked about Sanders ' remark at a May 11 hearing of the Senate intelligence committee .","depth":11},{"id":148,"text":"\" No , sir , that is not accurate , \"","depth":11},{"id":149,"text":"he said .","depth":11},{"id":150,"text":"McCabe called","depth":10},{"id":151,"text":"working with Comey \" the greatest privilege and honor of my professional life . \"","depth":10},{"id":152,"text":"McCabe , May 11 :","depth":10},{"id":153,"text":"`` I can tell you also","depth":12},{"id":154,"text":"that Director Comey enjoyed broad support within the FBI ,","depth":13},{"id":155,"text":"and still does to this day .","depth":13},{"id":156,"text":"We are a large organization .","depth":13},{"id":157,"text":"We are 36,500 people across this country , across this globe .","depth":13},{"id":158,"text":"We have a diversity of opinions about many things .","depth":13},{"id":159,"text":"But I can confidently tell you","depth":14},{"id":160,"text":"that the majority - the vast majority of FBI employees enjoyed a deep and positive connection to Director Comey . ''","depth":14},{"id":161,"text":"A day earlier , former FBI Deputy General Counsel Ernie Babcock told CNN ' s Jake Tapper","depth":10},{"id":162,"text":"that Comey \" created an atmosphere of integrity and transparency ,","depth":11},{"id":163,"text":"and , unfortunately , being transparent is now becoming a political football","depth":12},{"id":164,"text":"and one side or the other will not be happy","depth":13},{"id":165,"text":"if you actually do your job . \"","depth":13},{"id":166,"text":"Tapper , May 10 :","depth":11},{"id":167,"text":"`` How was morale at the FBI under Comey","depth":12},{"id":168,"text":"when you were there ? ''","depth":12},{"id":169,"text":"Babcock :","depth":12},{"id":170,"text":"`` It was outstanding .","depth":12},{"id":171,"text":"Jim Comey is an inclusive leader .","depth":13},{"id":172,"text":"He would not make","depth":14},{"id":173,"text":"and did not make critical decisions on his own","depth":15},{"id":174,"text":"as some other leaders do .","depth":15},{"id":175,"text":"He brought the senior staff together on a regular basis","depth":13},{"id":176,"text":"and included them in making any of the difficult decisions . ''","depth":13},{"id":177,"text":"This is obviously a developing story","depth":10},{"id":178,"text":"and more information likely will emerge .","depth":10},{"id":179,"text":"But what we know right now is that the White House ' s initial claim","depth":12},{"id":180,"text":"that the president acted","depth":13},{"id":181,"text":"based on Rosenstein ' s recommendation","depth":13},{"id":182,"text":"has been contradicted by the president himself .","depth":11},{"id":183,"text":"And its portrayal of Comey as having lost the confidence of the FBI rank and file is at best a matter of dispute .","depth":10},{"id":184,"text":"Trump threatens to cancel press briefings , unhappy with Comey coverage","depth":9},{"id":185,"text":"Trump :","depth":10},{"id":186,"text":"I planned to fire Comey","depth":11},{"id":187,"text":"regardless of Justice Department recommendation","depth":11},{"id":188,"text":"Deputy AG Rod Rosenstein to be invited to brief Senate on Comey 's firing","depth":10},{"id":189,"text":"Acting FBI Director Andrew McCabe :","depth":11},{"id":190,"text":"Comey 's firing wo n't impede Russia investigation","depth":11},{"id":191,"text":"Comey fired","depth":10},{"id":192,"text":"before Justice Department could complete internal probe into his election actions","depth":10}],"relations":[{"parent":385,"left":224,"right":384,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":224,"left":0,"right":223,"relation":"topic","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":223,"left":208,"right":222,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":208,"left":1,"right":207,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":207,"left":198,"right":206,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":198,"left":195,"right":197,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":195,"left":2,"right":194,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":194,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":197,"left":5,"right":196,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":196,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":206,"left":201,"right":205,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":201,"left":199,"right":200,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":199,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":200,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":205,"left":12,"right":204,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":204,"left":13,"right":203,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":203,"left":14,"right":202,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":202,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":222,"left":17,"right":221,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":221,"left":211,"right":220,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":211,"left":18,"right":210,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":210,"left":19,"right":209,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":209,"left":20,"right":21,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":220,